com.microblink.entities.recognizers.blinkid.generic

Class RecognitionModeFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microblink.entities.recognizers.blinkid.generic.RecognitionModeFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class RecognitionModeFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    RecognitionModeFilter is used to enable/disable recognition of specific document groups. Setting is taken into account only if the right for that document is purchased.
